package Net::Blossom::Server;

use strictures 2;

use Net::Blossom ();

our $VERSION = '0.001';

1;

=pod

=head1 NAME

Net::Blossom::Server - Server-side support for the Blossom protocol

=head1 SYNOPSIS

    use Net::Blossom::Server;

=head1 DESCRIPTION

C<Net::Blossom::Server> is currently a placeholder for the server-side
distribution. The server API is not defined yet.

Server support lives in a separate CPAN distribution so client users do not need
server, storage, daemon, or web framework dependencies.

=head1 STATUS

This module is scaffold-only. Do not build production server integrations
against it yet.

=cut
